body.p: The following Scandinavians bought or sold real estate in Chicago recently:
Sven O. Hawkinson to John Olson: Sacramento Avenue and 36th Street. Price, $750.
F. F. Schafers to Hedvig Sanders: Artesian Avenue and Hirsch Street. Price, $2,000.
Jacob Nielsen to L. Manning: Follansbee and Sacramento Avenues. Price, $6,150.
Rasmus Petersen to C. Jungian: Sacramento and Lyndale Avenues. Price, $3,500.
John L. Lewis to Peter Madsen Avenue and Hannover Street. Price, $1,550.
Emmanuel L. Petersen to Charles Bartell: B. & W. Subdivision, block 7, lots 9,
John A. Svendsen to Frank P. Jensen: Greenwood Terrace and 48th Avenue. Price, $1,000.
Ira H. Cobe to A. S. Johnson: Ridgeway Avenue and Grace Street. Price, $1,500.
G. A. Lyons to Jens Jensen: Ballou Street and Greenwood Terrace. Price, $8,900.
Jens Nordberg to S. Litsinger: 48th and Dickens Avenues. Price, $2,600.
A. Tomsen to J. C. Tomsen: Lawrence and Albany Avenues. Price, $1,500.
Nils P. Gron to L. H. Gulbrandsen: Humboldt Avenue and Ballou Street. Price, $1,900.
Oliane Olson to J. P. Andreason: Lawndale and Sundale Avenues. Price, $5,000.
Alexander Larsen to J. Wallace: Columbia and Kenmore Avenues. Price, $15,000.
L. G. Kirkland to L. P. Walters: Fargo and Kenmore Avenues. Price, $9,000.
